# .roadmap.hexa_chip — repo-overall tracker

> Cross-cutting state: invariant lattice, release cadence, cycle history,
> deadlines, pointers. Sister of `hexa-rtsc` / `hexa-codex` / `anima` under
> `dancinlab` org.

**Last sync**: 2026-05-08 (Phase C.5 complete · Phase D paused → hexa-embedded pivot) · **Current release**: v1.0.0 (v1.1.0 RSC code-layer FINAL on `main`) · **Branch**: `main`

---

## §0 Terminal goal — 28-verb chip substrate (7 그룹 모두 wired)

hexa-chip 도착지 = **28-verb semiconductor stack (architecture + design + process + packaging + accelerator + consciousness) 모두 working spec + 1+ 그룹 wired tape-out simulation**.

DoD:
1. `architecture` 그룹 ISA n=6 RTL gen 통합 .hexa.
2. `design` 그룹 EDA + RTL gen + verify-test 자동 pipeline.
3. `process` 그룹 wafer/yield n=6 closed-form fit (Samsung/SK/TSMC public).
4. `packaging` 그룹 advanced + 3D + HBM + interconnect.
5. `accelerator` 그룹 NPU + PIM + photonic 통합.
6. `consciousness` 그룹 chip + SoC anima cross-link.

## §A.1 Invariant lattice (n=6)

```
σ(6) · φ(6) = n · τ(6) = J₂ = 24
   12   ·   2  =  6  ·   4  = 24
```

| Symbol | Value | Role | Chip projection |
|--------|-------|------|-----------------|
| σ(6)   | 12    | sigma — cardinality bin | 12 process node generations (180nm → 2nm) |
| τ(6)   | 4     | tau — state quartet | 4 design stages (RTL / synth / P&R / sign-off) |
| φ(6)   | 2     | phi — verdict bit | digital / analog |
| J₂     | 24    | Mathieu / Leech | 24-layer interconnect stack ceiling |

